title: BILLY RAY CYRUS (1995) (Marvel Comics)
description:
A long time ago, in a comic book shop overfilled with a glut of Marvel product...

From the writer who created TUROK and the artist of FLASH GORDON...

Soon to be a huge Disney television star!
(not a minor supporting actor, not at all)...

Possibly the greatest single achievement in comic book history!

Worlds lived, worlds died, but sequential art was never the same...

BILLY RAY CYRUS #1 !!!

guest-starring THE DARK KNIGHT! (no, really)
